24
00:01:32,430 --> 00:01:33,310
Are you all right?

25
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:34,960
I'm fine.

26
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,790
Just that my presence seems

27
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,710
to have interrupted your private matters.

28
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,000
Judging by your condition,

29
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,680
