Your Highness.

40
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:36,560
Your Highness.

41
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:39,710
So, your childhood name

42
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:42,000
is Yao.

43
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,150
Your Highness.

44
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,360
Your Highness.

45
