Your Highness.

46
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,000
- Surround this place.
- Aye.

47
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,910
To have an affair
with the Emperor's intended consort,

48
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,910
I'd like to see
how you'll get out of it this time.

49
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:14,270
Hold on.

50
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,680
Third Prince, with such a big act,

51
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,520
what are you here for?

52
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,430
Is there something wrong
in the Palace of Yueying?

53
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,750
Are you playing dumb?

54
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,710
Are you insinuating something, Your Highness?

55
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,400
Please, do enlighten me.

56
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:35,710
I heard

57
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,800
that the Seventh Prince is in your palace now.

58
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:40,560
Being together in the dead of night.

59
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,000
Surely,

60
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,430
need I say more?

61
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,680
Third Prince, mind your words.

62
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,910
There's nothing
between me and the Seventh Prince.

63
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:50,360
If you keep slandering me

64
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:51,710
and ruining my reputation,

65
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,910
I shall seek justice from His Majesty.

66
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,520
Whether it is slander or not,

67
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,710
we shall see once we have a look inside.

68
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,360
Very well.

69
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:05,150
To prove my innocence,

70
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,120
please proceed.

71
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,310
Well, Your Highness,

72
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,310
did you find who you were looking for?

73
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,800
Princess Yingge, my apologies.

74
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:05,600
I was misled by the words of a vile servant,

75
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,160
and in my concern for the Princess's safety,

76
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,950
I acted rashly.

77
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,220
There is no need to trouble Father

78
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,270
with such a trivial matter.

79
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,630
Indeed, Your Highness.

80
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:20,870
But the vile slander caused no small trouble.

81
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:22,750
With such a commotion,

82
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:25,750
it would be difficult for me
to keep this incident hidden.

83
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,840
You worthless servant.

84
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,830
You've done more harm than good.

85
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,070
You shall pay for your crime today.

86
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:48,070
It's getting late.

87
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,560
I shall let you be, Princess.

88
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,200
Good night.

89
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,960
Go.

90
00:06:21,390 --> 00:06:22,230
Your Highness.

91
