♪Like a snowfall that blankets the ground♪

94
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:03,600
♪Creating an illusion of pure white all around♪

95
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,590
♪Each time the flowers bloom♪

96
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,430
♪They are destined♪

97
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:11,420
♪To wither and fade♪

98
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:14,330
♪Yet, unwilling to give in♪

99
