What do you mean? I am helping you.

108
00:07:40,570 --> 00:07:42,180
♪Never shattered♪

109
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:44,150
Your Highness.

110
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:51,490
♪Perhaps I'd never have understood♪

111
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:58,420
♪That despair is but an illusion♪

112
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,250
♪Love is like a blade♪

113
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:05,780
♪The thinner, the sharper♪

114
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:08,160
Please sweat it out.

115
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,750
Princess, you should leave now.

116
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,800
I can manage this myself.

117
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,160
Fine.

118
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:30,700
♪How to forget what once was♪

119
00:08:30,930 --> 00:08:37,920
♪The wounds of love pierce deep into the heart♪

120
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,280
Foolish move!

121
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:42,750
You acted rashly without certainty,

122
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,910
alerting the enemy.

123
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,350
Mother, please calm down.

124
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,550
It's all because of that wench

125
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,790
threatening to report to Father.

126
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:49,870
Father already favors her greatly.

127
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,720
I feared that if he found out about this,

128
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:54,080
he would punish me severely.

129
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:58,550
Indeed, the Third Prince is right.

130
00:08:58,910 --> 00:09:01,030
Given His Majesty's favor towards her,

131
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:04,120
it's too risky to act against her

132
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,390
under his watchful eyes.

133
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:09,120
We need to find a solution to this problem.

134
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,030
What's so difficult about that?

135
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:16,550
Once my son ascends to the throne,
all will be solved.

136
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,840
Your Highness, you mean…

137
00:09:27,700 --> 00:09:31,220
(Jiang He)

138
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:33,230
Princess,

139
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:35,150
may I have a word with you?

140
00:09:36,700 --> 00:09:37,990
(Jiang He, Huang Lian, the prescription)

141
00:09:43,750 --> 00:09:46,120
We hardly know each other, General.

142
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,200
It appears there's little for us to discuss.

143
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,720
It seems

144
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,910
the Princess is intentionally avoiding me.

145
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,320
Are you afraid I might discover something?

146
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,840
You must be kidding.

147
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,320
May I ask

148
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,870
what exactly you want to discuss?

149
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,150
Princess, you're from Yueying.

150
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,650
Coincidentally,
I too visited there years ago.

151
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,440
I was particularly impressed
with a candy shop on the east side of the city.

152
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,510
I wonder if you've been there.

153
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,200
I've lived in Yueying since childhood,

154
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,840
but I've never heard

155
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,390
of such a candy shop there.

156
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,910
If you're trying to test me,

157
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,200
I suggest you not waste your time.

158
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:23,000
I have matters to attend to,
so I'll take my leave now.

159
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:34,510
Yao,

160
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,200
you may pretend

161
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,480
to be Princess Yingge flawlessly,

162
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,630
but the birthmark on your neck

163
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:40,870
has been with you since childhood.

164
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,200
Yao,

165
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:46,390
what have you been through all these years?

166
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:47,870
When the Gu family fell,

167
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,960
I was away at war

168
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,600
and couldn't return in time.

169
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,910
It's a regret I'll carry for life.

170
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:55,910
I don't understand

171
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,390
what you are talking about.

172
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,270
Please mind your manners

173
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:00,840
and release me.

174
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:04,550
What are you doing here?

175
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,080
Seventh Prince.

176
00:11:08,430 --> 00:11:09,630
Since when did General Zhao Ming

177
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:11,390
become so familiar with Princess Yingge?

178
00:11:11,570 --> 00:11:12,440
I was…

179
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,840
The General was here at my invitation.

180
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,240
I greatly admire

181
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,630
his heroic deeds

182
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,840
and invited him over

183
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,790
to tell me the stories of the frontier.

184
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:23,390
Exactly.

185
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,630
The stories General Zhao shared

186
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,480
were fascinating.

187
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,390
I look forward to hearing more in the future.

188
00:11:31,510 --> 00:11:33,910
I shall take my leave now.

189
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,320
Am I interrupting

190
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,790
something between you two?

191
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,200
Please don't forget your place, Princess.

192
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,960
I'm going to check out Jiang He's residence.

193
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,680
Jiang He?

194
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,640
A subordinate of General Zhao Ming?

195
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,800
That's right.

196
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,030
Before Huang Lian died,

197
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,100
he mentioned Jiang He as someone

198
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,750
who knows the truth from years ago.

199
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,320
That's why it's worth a visit.

200
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:05,390
It seems everything is slowly coming to light.

201
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:10,440
Do you need to discuss that
with General Zhao Ming?

202
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:49,640
♪In the mire of deceit♪

203
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,470
♪Lies trap our fate♪

204
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:56,440
♪Love and hate entwined♪

205
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,780
♪Shattered by your sword, the knot unbinds♪

206
00:12:59,370 --> 00:13:02,500
♪Pear blossoms fall, leaving a tale of pain♪

207
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:06,440
♪Thoughts grow stronger, like a hidden flame♪

208
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:09,530
♪If all memories were to fade♪

209
00:13:09,530 --> 00:13:12,880
♪But longing remains♪

210
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:16,960
♪Let's bind our hearts together♪

211
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:19,850
♪Even in pain, let me draw near♪

212
00:13:19,850 --> 00:13:22,380
♪Can this fleeting sweetness linger♪

213
00:13:22,380 --> 00:13:26,500
♪Just a bit longer?♪

214
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:31,150
♪Cast our dreams into the fire's embrace♪

215
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:33,550
♪Let them end with a final grace♪

216
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:37,950
♪Burn away my memories of snow♪

217
00:13:37,950 --> 00:13:40,470
♪And the deceit♪

218
00:13:40,470 --> 00:13:44,790
♪Let me cherish one last look♪

219
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:47,140
♪In your gentle gaze♪

220
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:50,510
♪Our last kiss is so tender♪

221
